data.description:
Beautiful home with lots of charm and character. This home needs a little TLC sellers are still working on it but its move in ready. Two bedroom with 3 bathrooms. basement has a family room and a bonus room that could be a third bedroom. Home offers an nice kitchen with lots of beautiful cabinets with French doors  leading to a large room with many possibilities. Current use as a office/den.
The home has a nice bricked patio in the back and a garage  that is every mans dream with a large workshop. Nice fenced backyard for all those family gatherings.  Buyers to verify all information on MLS before making an offer.
